OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775675472
OL,3,CSuspected kidnap investigation after
OL,4,Cman allegedly forced into car
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a suspected
OL,7,Fkidnapping after a man was allegedly
OL,8,Fforced into a car against his will.
OL,10,FIt is believed the man was approached
OL,11,Fby a car on Manchester Road, Bolton,
OL,12,Fat around 4.30pm on 6 April where,
OL,13,Fafter engaging in conversation with
OL,14,Fits occupant, he was reportedly made
OL,15,Fto get into the car which then drove
OL,16,Fin the direction of the town centre.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
