PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775675472
OL,3,CSuspected kidnap investigation after
OL,4,Cman allegedly forced into car
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) say it
OL,7,Fis still investigating the full
OL,8,Fcircumstances of the incident and
OL,9,Fwould like to contact the man involved
OL,10,Fto check on his welfare.
OL,12,FHe is described as being approximately
OL,13,Faged in his 40s, around 5ft10, with a
OL,14,Fmedium build, bald, and no facial
OL,15,Fhair. He was dressed in all black,
OL,16,Fwith a black hoodie and black joggers,
OL,17,Fwhile speaking with a local accent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775675472
OL,3,CSuspected kidnap investigation after
OL,4,Cman allegedly forced into car
OL,6,FAnyone who witnessed the incident or
OL,7,Fbelieves they have information are
OL,8,Falso asked to get in touch - either
OL,9,Fdirectly, or anonymously.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Liam Carolan, from
OL,12,FGMP's Bolton district, said: "We have
OL,13,Fconducted initial enquiries, and we
OL,14,Fbelieve that a man may have been a
OL,15,Fvictim of a crime, and we are very
OL,16,Fkeen to speak to him to find out what
OL,17,Fhappened.
OL,26,@tD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
