PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775675472
OL,3,CSuspected kidnap investigation after
OL,4,Cman allegedly forced into car
OL,6,F"I would like to urge this man, or
OL,7,Fanybody who knows him and may have
OL,8,Fspoken to him about what happened, to
OL,9,Fplease contact the police.
OL,11,F"You can contact us via 101 quoting
OL,12,Flog 2080 of 06/04/2026, or through the
OL,13,FLiveChat function at gmp.police.uk.
OL,14,FAlternatively, you can contact
OL,15,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,16,F111."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@EO]
